1- A 72-year-old male from Alqrayat (Alkurayat) [Al Jawf region]. [Reported as a newly confirmed case on 11 Jan 2018 at which time he was noted to be in stable condition. Classified as a primary case with high risk exposure history still under investigation. - Mod.MPP]

